OL,5, Nearly one in five teachers in England 
OL,6, has been hit by a pupil this year, a   
OL,7, survey commissioned by the BBC says.   
OL,9,FOne teacher told BBC News behaviour was
OL,10,Fa "never-ending battle". Another said  
OL,11,Fspitting, swearing and chair-throwing  
OL,12,Fwere among the things happening often. 
OL,14,FA union says its members are reporting 
OL,15,Fworsening violence and abuse from      
OL,16,Fpupils since the Covid pandemic.       
OL,18,FThe Department for Education (DfE) says
OL,19,Fit has invested #10m in behaviour hubs 
OL,20,Fto support schools.                    
